{
  "skippable": false,
  "sprites": {
    "bg": {
      "comment": "Fondo negro que cubre toda la pantalla durante la transición",
      "type": "rect",
      "color": "0xFF000000",
      "width": 2,
      "height": 2,
      "x": -100,
      "y": -100,
      "scrollFactor": 0,
      "alpha": 1
    },
    "cutsceneCan": {
      "comment": "Bote de spray que vuela por el aire al ser pateado",
      "type": "sparrow",
      "image": "game/weekend/wked1_cutscene_1_can",
      "x": 950,
      "y": 725,
      "scrollFactor": 1,
      "antialiasing": true,
      "animations": [
        {
          "name": "up",
          "prefix": "can kicked up0",
          "fps": 24,
          "loop": false
        },
        {
          "name": "forward",
          "prefix": "can kick quick0",
          "fps": 24,
          "loop": false
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "steps": [
    {
      "comment": "──────────── SETUP ────────────"
    },
    {
      "action": "setCamVisible",
      "cam": "hud",
      "visible": false,
      "duration": 0.4,
      "async": true
    },
    {
      "action": "add",
      "sprite": "bg"
    },
    {
      "comment": "FIX: el zoom/move a Pico fue eliminado — la cámara usa la posición default del stage al arrancar"
    },
    {
      "comment": "FIX: zoom y posición iniciales eliminados — la cámara arranca en el default del stage"
    },
    {
      "comment": "Pico muestra su cara de pocos amigos"
    },
    {
      "action": "stageAnim",
      "sprite": "bf",
      "anim": "intro1",
      "force": true
    },
    {
      "comment": "Esperar 0.7s y arrancar la música de cutscene"
    },
    {
      "action": "wait",
      "time": 0.7
    },
    {
      "comment": "Música de cutscene — music:true usa Paths.music() en vez de Paths.sound().",
      "comment2": "Pon el archivo en: mods/tuMod/music/darnellCanCutscene.ogg",
      "action": "playSound",
      "key": "darnellCanCutscene/darnellCanCutscene",
      "music": true,
      "volume": 1.0,
      "id": "cutsceneMusic",
      "stage": true
    },
    {
      "comment": "Fade out del negro de fondo (async — no bloquea)"
    },
    {
      "action": "tween",
      "sprite": "bg",
      "props": {
        "alpha": 0
      },
      "duration": 2.0,
      "async": true
    },
    {
      "comment": "──────────── CÁMARA SE ALEJA HACIA DARNELL (delay = 2.0s desde el inicio) ────────────"
    },
    {
      "comment": "Esperar 1.3s más para llegar a t=2.0 total"
    },
    {
      "action": "wait",
      "time": 1.3
    },
    {
      "comment": "Zoom out a 0.66 + pan hacia Darnell — ambos async para que ocurran en paralelo.",
      "comment2": "camX/Y son scroll coords: focusPoint - screenHalf. Ver phillyStreets.json."
    },
    {
      "action": "cameraZoom",
      "zoom": 0.66,
      "duration": 2.5,
      "ease": "quadInOut",
      "async": true
    },
    {
      "action": "cameraPan",
      "camX": 800,
      "camY": 400,
      "duration": 2.5,
      "ease": "quadInOut",
      "async": true
    },
    {
      "comment": "──────────── DARNELL ENCIENDE EL BOTE (t=5.0) ────────────"
    },
    {
      "action": "wait",
      "time": 3.0
    },
    {
      "action": "stageAnim",
      "sprite": "dad",
      "anim": "lightCan",
      "force": true
    },
    {
      "action": "playSound",
      "key": "Darnell_Lighter",
      "volume": 1.0,
      "stage": true
    },
    {
      "comment": "──────────── PICO AMARTILLA + CÁMARA SHIFT (t=6.0) ────────────"
    },
    {
      "action": "wait",
      "time": 1.0
    },
    {
      "action": "cameraPan",
      "camX": 1020,
      "camY": 400,
      "duration": 0.5,
      "ease": "quadInOut",
      "async": true
    },
    {
      "action": "stageAnim",
      "sprite": "bf",
      "anim": "cock",
      "force": true
    },
    {
      "action": "playSound",
      "key": "Gun_Prep",
      "volume": 1.0,
      "stage": true
    },
    {
      "comment": "──────────── DARNELL PATEA EL BOTE (t=6.4) ────────────"
    },
    {
      "action": "wait",
      "time": 0.4
    },
    {
      "action": "stageAnim",
      "sprite": "dad",
      "anim": "kickCan",
      "force": true
    },
    {
      "action": "playSound",
      "key": "Kick_Can_UP",
      "volume": 1.0,
      "stage": true
    },
    {
      "action": "add",
      "sprite": "cutsceneCan"
    },
    {
      "action": "playAnim",
      "sprite": "cutsceneCan",
      "anim": "up"
    },
    {
      "comment": "──────────── DARNELL RODILLAZO (t=6.9) ────────────"
    },
    {
      "action": "wait",
      "time": 0.5
    },
    {
      "action": "stageAnim",
      "sprite": "dad",
      "anim": "kneeCan",
      "force": true
    },
    {
      "action": "playSound",
      "key": "Kick_Can_FORWARD",
      "volume": 1.0,
      "stage": true
    },
    {
      "action": "playAnim",
      "sprite": "cutsceneCan",
      "anim": "forward"
    },
    {
      "comment": "──────────── PICO DISPARA — EXPLOSIÓN (t=7.1) ────────────"
    },
    {
      "action": "wait",
      "time": 0.2
    },
    {
      "action": "stageAnim",
      "sprite": "bf",
      "anim": "intro2",
      "force": true
    },
    {
      "comment": "Disparo — en JSON no hay random, usa una variante fija. Cambia el número 1-4 a mano.",
      "action": "playSound",
      "key": "shot1",
      "volume": 1.0,
      "stage": true
    },
    {
      "action": "remove",
      "sprite": "cutsceneCan"
    },
    {
      "action": "cameraFlash",
      "color": "WHITE",
      "duration": 0.25,
      "async": true
    },
    {
      "comment": "──────────── DARNELL RÍE (t=7.9) ────────────"
    },
    {
      "action": "wait",
      "time": 0.8
    },
    {
      "action": "cameraPan",
      "camX": 800,
      "camY": 400,
      "duration": 0.5,
      "ease": "quadInOut",
      "async": true
    },
    {
      "action": "stageAnim",
      "sprite": "dad",
      "anim": "laughCutscene",
      "force": true
    },
    {
      "action": "playSound",
      "key": "cutscene/darnell_laugh",
      "volume": 0.6,
      "stage": true
    },
    {
      "comment": "──────────── NENE RÍE (t=8.2) ────────────"
    },
    {
      "action": "wait",
      "time": 0.3
    },
    {
      "action": "stageAnim",
      "sprite": "gf",
      "anim": "laughCutscene",
      "force": true
    },
    {
      "action": "playSound",
      "key": "cutscene/nene_laugh",
      "volume": 0.6,
      "stage": true
    },
    {
      "comment": "──────────── CÁMARA VUELVE A POSICIÓN NORMAL + FIN (t=10.0) ────────────"
    },
    {
      "action": "wait",
      "time": 1.8
    },
    {
      "comment": "Zoom vuelve a 0.77 (defaultZoom de phillyStreets) + pan a posición final de Darnell",
      "comment2": "camX 300 = darnellFocus+180-640 (mismo que V-Slice 'darnellPos[0]+180')"
    },
    {
      "action": "cameraZoom",
      "zoom": 0.77,
      "duration": 2.0,
      "ease": "sineInOut",
      "async": true
    },
    {
      "action": "wait",
      "time": 0.1
    },
    {
      "action": "remove",
      "sprite": "bg"
    },
    {
      "action": "end"
    }
  ]
}